       exe-exp-prs-dat-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Esportazione [ref]                                        *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       exe-exp-ref-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Preparazione file area generica                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "xpg "               to   f-xxx-are              .
           move      "ref "               to   f-xxx-nam              .
           move      "std_xpg_ref"        to   f-xxx-npe              .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Richiesta di conferma, se manuale               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   ric-cnf-man-000      thru ric-cnf-man-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
